=== QUANTUM_FORGE ===
# id: 75
# title: The Quantum Forge
# chinese_title: 量子锻炉
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

A shimmering forge hangs suspended in a zero-gravity chamber, its surface rippling with quantum fluctuations. Around it, characters float like embers — radicals breaking apart and recombining. The forge seems to respond to linguistic intent, reshaping matter based on the meaning of characters spoken near it.

* [Speak a character of creation into the forge]
  ~ gain_radical("金")
  "锻" (duàn) — to forge, to temper. The radical "金" (jīn) means metal.
* [Feed the forge raw materials] {requires: gold >= 20}
  ~ gain_equipment
  "造" (zào) — to create, to build
* [Study the quantum-linguistic phenomenon]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "量" (liáng) — to measure, quantum
